snippet.title: Atlas gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Atlas, Dos PC game produced by Sunflowers in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/atlas/6818/
Watching the introduction and having a quick look at the interface of this strategy/trading German game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Aces of the Pacific - https://youtu.be/vkIG8Iuzsdo

Merchant Colony - https://youtu.be/VzZjsAOWl3w
